title: IntroCRT
---
// # I hate sentinal values but hey

<<if is_bool_set("first_door", "locked")>>
  LLManager: Hm, it seems like the door may be locked, let's see what I can do.
  <<toggle_value "first_door" "locked">>
  LLManager: Hopefully this worked, otherwise I'll need to call HR to find a replacement for you.
<<endif>>

<<if get_current_objective() == "">>
  LLManager: Good morning, valued employee. You have been working with us for 450 days.
  LLManager: Thank you for your continued productivity, if you keep this up you might get a promotion.
  LLManager: Which means two pizza parties per month.
  LLManager: Before you get to work you should socialise to your fellow employees.
  LLManager: It is employee No.6's birthday. Please go and congratulate them.
  LLManager: It is important to celebrate milestones to ensure worker productivity.

  <<create_objective "socialisation" "Socialise" 0.0>>
  <<create_subobjective "soc_1" "Congratulate employee No.6" "socialisation">>

  <<create_objective "talk_to_llm" "Talk to LLManager again" 1.0>>
<<elseif get_current_objective() == "socialisation">>
  LLManager: Please engage in socialisation with your fellow employees.
<<elseif get_current_objective() == "talk_to_llm">>
  <<complete_objective "talk_to_llm">>

  LLManager: Well done, you have engaged in productivity boosting activities.
  LLManager: Please take your mandated fifteen minute mental health break.
  LLManager: Just up the stairs and to the left, and then up the stairs and to the left...
  LLManager: And then up the stairs and to the left...
  LLManager: And then up the stairs and to the left...
  LLManager: Be sure to set a timer so you don't accidentally waste time.
  LLManager: Remember, a productive mind is a happy mind.

  <<create_objective "breakroom" "Take a mental health break." 2.0>>
<<endif>>
